This is a simple and easy to use strategy for low-volatility stocks. It prints a BUY or SELL signal to alert you that certain conditions have been met. I use it as a time saver to help identify which charts I need to look at. You can adjust the inputs and properties to suit your needs. I would suggest allowing two or three orders.

